Mat - Mat中的类
The Mat class provides a Java interface to the M-functions from the files: H:\\Program Files\\MATLAB\\R2012a\\bin\\matrix.m H:\\Program Files\\MATLAB\\R2012a\\bin\\tensorsvd.m The Mat.dispose() method must be called on a Mat instance when it is no longer needed to ensure that native resources allocated by this class are properly freed.

MatRemote - Mat中的接口
The MatRemote class provides a Java RMI-compliant interface to the M-functions from the files: H:\\Program Files\\MATLAB\\R2012a\\bin\\matrix.m H:\\Program Files\\MATLAB\\R2012a\\bin\\tensorsvd.m The dispose() method must be called on a MatRemote instance when it is no longer needed to ensure that native resources allocated by this class are properly freed, and the server-side proxy is unexported.
